50|$|The AU {{claims that}} its mandate {{in the area}} of peace and {{security}} is valid for the whole African continent. In addition to this, several Regional Economic Communities (RECs) and Regional Mechanisms (RMs) are part of the APSA. The cooperation between the RECs and the AU is guided by the <b>principles</b> <b>of</b> <b>subsidiarity,</b> <b>of</b> complementarity and of the comparative advantages.The operationalisation of the APSA Instruments was intended to be finished until the end of 2015. However, the status of the instruments varies strongly depending on the individual instruments and organisation.|$|R
